item.dc:creator: @liamsford liamsford
item.description:
@liamsford wrote:

Go to www.No-ip.com

Make an account

Log in

Go to the “add” button

Add a server name

Go to control pannel for your computer

Go to your fire wall

Open a port named your full server ip for port’s 43594 and 5555
